Class Plane

  • java.lang.Object
    • Plane

  • public class Plane
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Plane that can seat individual Passengers and Passengers in a Group. It can also add and remove these Passengers and Groups. It also has a method to help populate the Plane from prior program runs.

      boolean addGroup(Group group, java.lang.String serviceClass)
      This method uses a helper method to find the first row of adjacent seats in a seat row that is sufficient to accommodate the group, or if no such seat row exists, finds the row with the largest number of adjacent seats in any seat row, fills it up with members of the group, and repeats that process (finding the row with the largest number of adjacent seats) until all members of the group have been seated.

      • removePassenger

        public boolean removePassenger(java.lang.String name)
        Cancels a Passengers reservation from the Plane. It returns true if Passenger is successfully removed from the Plane or false if Passenger was not removed from the Plane because it belonged to a Group. Individual Passengers from a Group cannot cancel their reservation.
        Parameters:
        name - name of the Passenger to be removed
        Returns:
        true if Passenger is successfully removed from the Plane or false if Passenger was not removed from the Plane, because it belonged to a Group

      • addGroup

        public boolean addGroup(Group group,
                        java.lang.String serviceClass)
        This method uses a helper method to find the first row of adjacent seats in a seat row that is sufficient to accommodate the group, or if no such seat row exists, finds the row with the largest number of adjacent seats in any seat row, fills it up with members of the group, and repeats that process (finding the row with the largest number of adjacent seats) until all members of the group have been seated. If there is insufficient space to seat all members of the group, none should be seated.
        Parameters:
        group -
        serviceClass -
        Returns:
        true if Group was successfully added or false if Group could not be seated

      • removeGroup

        public boolean removeGroup(java.lang.String group_name)
        Cancels a Group reservation removing all the members of the Group from the plane.
        Parameters:
        group_name - name of the group to be removed
        Returns:
        true if Group was successfully removed or false if Group could not be removed
